      "description": "Choose Enlarge or Reduce. An unwilling creature can make a Constitution save to negate the spell. Enlarge: target size +1, Advantage on Strength checks and saves, +1d4 damage with enlarged weapons or Unarmed Strikes. Reduce: target size -1, Disadvantage on Strength checks and saves, -1d4 damage with reduced weapons or Unarmed Strikes, minimum 1 damage.",
